Michael Dornemann

Age : 70Public asset : 1,202,992 USDLinked companies :  Take Two Interactive Software Inc 





Summary 



Mr. Michael Dornemann is Lead Independent Director at Take-Two Interactive Software, Inc., Chairman at Crossing Pictures GmbH, and Chairman at Strenesse AG.He is on the Board of Directors at Take-Two Interactive Software, Inc.Mr. Dornemann was previously employed as Vice Chairman by Access Worldwide Communications, Inc., Chief Executive Officer by BMG RIGHTS MANAGEMENT GmbH, and Chief Executive Officer by BMG Entertainment.He also served on the board at Bertelsmann SE & Co. KGaA, Nippon Columbia Co., Ltd., Jet Set AG, and DirectoryM, Inc.



