Individual




Michael Dornemann



Mr. Michael Dornemann is Lead Independent Director at Take-Two Interactive Software, Inc., Chairman at Crossing Pictures GmbH and Chairman at Strenesse AG. He is on the Board of Directors at Take-Two Interactive Software, Inc. Mr. Dornemann was previously employed as Vice Chairman by Access Worldwide Communications, Inc., Chief Executive Officer by BMG Entertainment, and Chief Executive Officer by BMG Rights Management GmbH. He also served on the board at Bertelsmann SE & Co. KGaA, DirectoryM, Inc., Jet Set AG and Nippon Columbia Co., Ltd.



